## Usage

{% if design.transport == "http" %}
This server runs over HTTP (streamable). Connect to it at the configured endpoint.

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "{{ design.server_name }}": {
      "url": "http://localhost:{{ design.http_port }}/sse"
    }
  }
}
```
{% else %}
This server runs over stdio. Add it to your MCP client config:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "{{ design.server_name }}": {
      "command": "mcp-{{ design.server_name | kebab_case }}"
    }
  }
}
```
{% endif %}
